	<div class="tabContent" id="goals">
    <div class='tabtext'>
      <h2>Our Goals</h2>
		  <h3>The Learning Shelter will:</h3>
		  <ul>
			  <li>Expose learners to possibilities via hands on experience with various technologies including; 3D printing, laser cutting, welding, CAD Design, Web Design and Development</li>
			  <li>Empower learners to develop a physical and digital identity</li>
			  <li>Provide a daily structure for learners to develop technical and interpersonal skills</li>
			  <li>Enable learners to build and present hardware or software prototypes</li>
			  <li>Assist learners with setting goals for personal and professional development</li>
		  </ul>
    </div>
	</div>

